Package: luadns-ddns
Architecture: any
Pre-Depends:
 debconf (>=1.5.77),
Depends:
 bind9-dnsutils (>=9.0),
 gawk (>=5.0),
 bash (>=5.0),
 coreutils (>=8.32),
 curl (>=7.8),
 ${misc:Depends},
Suggests:
 mutt (>=2.2),
Description: Simple Bash DDNS Script using Luadns.com
 Checks for a public IP change and updates a record at
 Luadns.com if one is found.
 Email Notification functionality included.
 Requires control of a domain using Luadns.com for DNS hosting.
 Supports also the use of a custom notification hook as an
 alternative to standard emails.

